narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Met's Transportation Services LLC is a Non-emergency Medical Transport (VAN) provider based in La Place, LA. From 2024-04 through 2024-12, this provider received $154K in Medicaid payments across 2K claims serving 481 beneficiaries, billing 1 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: Bills 3.9× the national median for T2003 (T2003), at $85 per claim vs. the median of $22. This places them well above the 99th percentile nationally.
100% of billing is concentrated in T2003 (T2003), indicating significant specialization in this service.
